'''亞歷山大·「艾力克斯」·德雷珀·沃爾夫'''（英語：'''Alexander "Alex" Draper Wolff'''；{{bd|1997年|11月1日|||catIdx=W}}）<ref> [http://www.tvguide.com/celebrities/alex-wolff/285673 "Alex Wolff: Biography"]. TVGuide.com. [https://web.archive.org/web/20160401191055/http://www.tvguide.com/celebrities/alex-wolff/285673/ Archived] from the original on April 1, 2016. Retrieved March 10, 2014.</ref>，又名「艾力克斯·沃爾夫」，是一位[[美國|美國]][[男演員|男演員]]、歌手、創作歌手、作曲家、鍵盤手和吉他手，因出演2016年《[[我的希臘婚禮2|我的希臘婚禮2]]》之電影作品而聞名，此時，他還是演員[[納特·沃爾夫|納特·沃爾夫]]的弟弟。

==生平==
艾力克斯出生於紐約曼哈頓，他是爵士鋼琴家{{le|麥可·沃爾夫|Michael Wolff}}和女演員{{le|波利·德雷珀|Polly Draper}}的兒子，父親是[[猶太人|猶太人]]<ref>{{cite web|first=Mitchell|last=Seidel|url=https://jazztimes.com/departments/at-home/michael-wolff/|title=Michael Wolff|work=JazzTimes|date=September 1, 2007|accessdate=May 12, 2018|archive-date=2018-06-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180617142223/https://jazztimes.com/departments/at-home/michael-wolff/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|first=Alan|last=Smason|url=https://www.clevelandjewishnews.com/archives/cleveland-set-to-enjoy-smooth-jazz-stylings-of-michael-wolff/article_c2b4cf33-f85a-54de-a073-0908e4884335.html|title=Cleveland set to enjoy smooth jazz stylings of Michael Wolff|work=Cleveland Jewish News|date=November 3, 2006|accessdate=May 12, 2018|archive-date=2016-04-05|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6gXzoNREc?url=http://www.clevelandjewishnews.com/archives/cleveland-set-to-enjoy-smooth-jazz-stylings-of-michael-wolff/article_c2b4cf33-f85a-54de-a073-0908e4884335.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.jweekly.com/2007/05/18/celebrity-jews-121/|title=Celebrity Jews|work=J. The Jewish News of Northern California|date=May 18, 2007|accessdate=May 12, 2018|archive-date=2018-05-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180513080908/https://www.jweekly.com/2007/05/18/celebrity-jews-121/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，而母親是基督教徒<ref name=jewishnews2>{{cite web|url=http://www.crescentcityjewishnews.com/jeff-berlin-to-join-wolfe-and-clark-expedition-here/|title=Jeff Berlin to join Wolff and Clark Expedition here|last=Smason|first=Alan|work=Crescent City Jewish News|date=March 8, 2013|accessdate=May 12, 2018|archive-date=2018-06-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180617165114/https://www.crescentcityjewishnews.com/jeff-berlin-to-join-wolfe-and-clark-expedition-here/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，他還有一名哥哥叫[[納特·沃爾夫|納特·沃爾夫]]，也是一名演員和歌手，他的外祖父是風險投資客和公民領袖威廉·亨利·德雷珀三世<ref>Europa Publications (2003). The International Who's Who 2004. Routledge. p. 454. ISBN 1857432177.</ref>，與哥哥[[納特·沃爾夫|納特·沃爾夫]]一樣是身為投資客的{{le|提姆·德雷珀|Tim Draper}}的侄子<ref>Saracevic, Al (January 26, 2007). [http://www.sfgate.com/cgi-bin/blogs/sfgate/detail?blogid=19&entry_id=12989 "The Technology Chronicles: Six degrees of Tim Draper"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.sfgate.com/cgi-bin/blogs/sfgate/detail?blogid=19&entry_id=12989 |date=20090202154419 }}. SFGate. Retrieved January 16, 2012.</ref>、女星{{le|潔西·德雷珀|Jesse Draper}}的表弟和身為銀行家<ref> Lee, Felicia R. (January 25, 2007). [http://www.nytimes.com/2007/01/25/arts/television/25nake.html "A TV Family Bound by Blood and a Band"]. The New York Times. Retrieved March 10, 2014.</ref>，艾力克斯也是外交官{{le|小威廉·亨利·德雷珀|William Henry Draper Jr.}}的曾孫<ref>Lim, Jason (June 3, 2011). [http://technode.com/2011/06/03/tim-draper-is-the-risk-master/ "Baidu Early Investor, Tim Draper is the Risk Master"] {{Wayback|url=http://technode.com/2011/06/03/tim-draper-is-the-risk-master/ |date=20120124172026 }}. TechNode.com. Retrieved January 16, 2012.</ref><ref>P.V, Sahad (October 16, 2008). [http://www.vccircle.com/500/news/next-tech-giant-will-be-a-cellphone-application-company-tim-draper "Next Tech Giant Will Be A Cellphone Application Company: Tim Draper"] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160316191630/http://www.vccircle.com/news/telecom/2008/10/15/next-tech-giant-will-be-cellphone-application-company-tim-draper |date=2016-03-16 }}. VCCircle.com. [https://web.archive.org/web/20160316191630/http://www.vccircle.com/news/telecom/2008/10/15/next-tech-giant-will-be-cellphone-application-company-tim-draper Archived] from the original on March 16, 2016. Retrieved January 16, 2012.</ref>。

